{"tid":1250181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(急求！)大規模林鄭政績宣傳","createTime":"2019-06-22T03:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T09:49:06.000Z","uid":72795,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3128b4ad87f3a8e5c7db2b0da57aef0f49757ae9","tid":1250181,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"參考TRUMP，成功的輿論一定要有鋪天蓋地的事實報導<br />\n林鄭在２年多的執政，經濟/民生方面一定有好多缺點<br />\n我地應該將缺點放大，而且用中立報導方式同全港人分享<br />\n舉例：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">-林鄭執政２年　學生自殺率暴升５倍<br />\n-林鄭冷血 綜緩每年減批1000老弱病人<br />\n-林鄭理財不當 庫房XXXX</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n拋蛋引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa33a8a89605e17f973e4c3fde4eeacfe07a0fec","tid":1250181,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ddcb2e5ed1fe24eb6497faa348637570219ec7","tid":1250181,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f299a2c3786bb3c4b143f917abd854e0e3775e","tid":1250181,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc00ad018afa94bcbc7bdead3a39c4a8afebae74","tid":1250181,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>統計處</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/index_tc.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Findex_tc.jsp&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bhwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D